<TD ALIGN=CENTER WIDTH=120 BGCOLOR="#DDDDDD"><FONT CLASS=GraphicCaption>"Luclin does nothing for me. There's no point in picking a new face when you're The Faceless to begin with."</FONT></TD>
<TD BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF"><IMG SRC="images/spacer.gif"></TD>
